AskSensors supports networkable micro-controllers, bridges and materials inclusing ESP8266, Arduino, Raspberry Pi and more.
Feel free to connect your own hardware to AskSensors, and share it with the community!

Tested platforms:

1) Arduino: Arduino Uno, Nano, Mini, Due, Mega, etc
2) ESP8266: Generic, NodeMCU, Huzzah, etc.
3) ESP32.
4) Raspberry Pi.
5) Node.js: on Regular PC with Linux / macOS/ Windows and browsers

